snippet.textDisplay: Raps supporter since 2001. Gone are the dark days. From our struggling days with our old core, from VC to Bosh to DD & company, Kawhi You wont be forgotten. Thank You for bringing the LB trophy to Canada & to us real fans that never gave up on our team. I was in attendance at the game of Game 7 against Philly with my Dad & we'll never forget that shot ever in our lives. I hang a championship poster of this roster in my home & will never take it down. Real fans & Canadians appreciate you brother. Much respect. Enjoy LA, your home & family.
